{"id": "ChIJIwZRwD66woAR92DUPV7Lw9A", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 731, "displayName": {"text": "Copenhagen Pastry", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Danish bakeshop offering traditional breads, cakes & pastries in contemporary digs.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJIwZRwD66woAR92DUPV7Lw9A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGRVSlhMVTVhTkZOemJGaG1XVVo0U1d0cVdHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Copenhagen Pastry is a gem. I love the Scandinavian simplicity of the design — elegant, bright, and welcoming both inside and out. The Princess Cake was absolutely outstanding — soft sponge, perfectly balanced custard and raspberry jam, and that light almond layer on top was perfection. The owner was very attentive, and the service was smooth and genuine. You can feel the care in every detail.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Copenhagen Pastry is a gem. I love the Scandinavian simplicity of the design — elegant, bright, and welcoming both inside and out. The Princess Cake was absolutely outstanding — soft sponge, perfectly balanced custard and raspberry jam, and that light almond layer on top was perfection. The owner was very attentive, and the service was smooth and genuine. You can feel the care in every detail.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alex S", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101840471363858217207/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJU4gnmLKXyAOSDK3lv7UfJCQrunkWy0yiNjlMaUCvIEWnpGLk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-01T22:07:05.470755905Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGRVSlhMVTVhTkZOemJGaG1XVVo0U1d0cVdHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2prNGRVSlhMVTVhTkZOemJGaG1XVVo0U1d0cVdHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2ba3ec0510623:0xd0c3cb5e3dd460f7"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIwZRwD66woAR92DUPV7Lw9A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWVHVmZObTU1Vm5wVFV6RTRSaTFGYURWMlZsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "11 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This bakery is named after a city in Denmark, therefore it is a danish bakery. I really love the aesthetic. It’s very crisp and clean. Everything is very neat and simple. All the pastries are laid out and you can easily pick and the aesthetic is pristine. The cakes are so tasty and luscious and moist definitely worth a try. I can’t imagine being disappointedthis service is good as well. There’s always someone there who is attentive. I never have to wait long.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This bakery is named after a city in Denmark, therefore it is a danish bakery. I really love the aesthetic. It’s very crisp and clean. Everything is very neat and simple. All the pastries are laid out and you can easily pick and the aesthetic is pristine. The cakes are so tasty and luscious and moist definitely worth a try. I can’t imagine being disappointedthis service is good as well. There’s always someone there who is attentive. I never have to wait long.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Miranda Jeanette", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103026857280178388607/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDKtMMk5K7Zz6qEr0eQ3WTYKckUmESmRtKkeax4OzBKY5dweEs7A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-12T06:23:23.811601281Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWVHVmZObTU1Vm5wVFV6RTRSaTFGYURWMlZsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWVHVmZObTU1Vm5wVFV6RTRSaTFGYURWMlZsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2ba3ec0510623:0xd0c3cb5e3dd460f7"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIwZRwD66woAR92DUPV7Lw9A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Sc1JHUm5ibGwwV1MxU1lrTjRNWE5HVXpKV2VFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We ordered a Hazelnut chocolate cake for my husband’s birthday party and EVERYONE loved the cake. It was very fresh, light and not sweet at all, it had a perfect balance of everything. Even our picky kids said it was really good. Thank you so much for the delicious cake and great service!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We ordered a Hazelnut chocolate cake for my husband’s birthday party and EVERYONE loved the cake. It was very fresh, light and not sweet at all, it had a perfect balance of everything. Even our picky kids said it was really good. Thank you so much for the delicious cake and great service!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elena Petrova", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108831114941190443531/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUORbGKOE5mid1WX4KddALbvQ2GJDcIrei2PAyUbnh6JqHs3QAp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-02T04:02:36.371776793Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Sc1JHUm5ibGwwV1MxU1lrTjRNWE5HVXpKV2VFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Sc1JHUm5ibGwwV1MxU1lrTjRNWE5HVXpKV2VFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2ba3ec0510623:0xd0c3cb5e3dd460f7"}, {"name": "places/ChIJIwZRwD66woAR92DUPV7Lw9A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOQ2NYQTNTR3hMT1hSVU5IVmlieTE2U25OV2IyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is really good. I am European, so my pastry standards are high enough. This blueberry thing is great!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is really good. I am European, so my pastry standards are high enough. This blueberry thing is great!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttri